text: KBOI may refer to: * KBOI (AM), a radio station (670 AM) licensed to Boise, Idaho, United States * KQFC, a radio station (97.9 FM) licensed to Boise, Idaho, United States, which used the call sign KBOI-FM from 1960 to 1985 * KBOI-TV, a television station (channel 28 digital/2 virtual) licensed to Boise, Idaho, United States * Boise Airport (ICAO code KBOI)
title: KBOI
